{
  "total_duration": 739.99,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.336,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Olympic Games"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“奥林匹克运动会”。但这课不是让我们背一堆 Olympic sports。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 9.686,
      "end": 17.086,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它更像一张 city-building countdown，奥运会还有 four years，可是整座城市现在就要开始准备。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 17.436,
      "end": 27.34,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Olympic Games will be held in our country in four years' time."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话先给出未来的大事件：四年后，奥运会要在这个国家举行。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 27.689,
      "end": 38.185,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么要提前这么久？因为"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a great many people"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "will visit the country。Athletes, teams, reporters, and visitors 都要来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 38.535,
      "end": 53.495,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以城市要有 hotels 给游客住，要有 an immense stadium 给比赛用，要有 an"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Olympic-standard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "swimming pool，也要有 roads and a railway line 让人群移动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 53.845,
      "end": 62.525,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Olympic-standard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“像奥运一样好看”，而是 good enough to meet Olympic requirements，达到奥运会要求的标准。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 62.875,
      "end": 77.075,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以把这课看成一张地图加时间线：capital 旁边有 Olympic City；now 开始建；by the end of this year roads 完成；by the end of next year stadium 完成；in four years' time the Games arrive。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 77.424,
      "end": 94.984,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：four years -> visitors -> government -> hotels, stadium, pool -> roads, railway -> Olympic City -> roads this year -> stadium next year -> designed buildings -> watch anxiously -> look forward -> never held before。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 95.334,
      "end": 102.998,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是未来事件和城市问题。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Olympic Games will be held in our country in four years' time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 103.348,
      "end": 113.62,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be held"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 future passive，意思是“将会举行”。不是某个人一个人办，而是这个国家会承办这件大事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 113.97,
      "end": 121.994,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文马上解释原因："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As a great many people will be visiting the country"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，会有大量的人来到这里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 122.344,
      "end": 134.24,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a great many people"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 a very large number of people。奥运会来的不只是运动员，还有 team members, reporters, volunteers, and visitors。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 134.589,
      "end": 141.029,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以第一幅画要问：如果全世界的人四年后要来，一座城市现在需要准备什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 141.379,
      "end": 150.811,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是政府的建设计划。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The government will be building new hotels, an immense stadium, and a new Olympic-standard swimming pool."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 151.161,
      "end": 161.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "government"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不要讲成政治话题。它就是组织公共项目的 public authority，可以修路、建体育馆、安排交通。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 162.119,
      "end": 170.287,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be building"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示 future work in progress。四年之前的这段时间里，建设会一直进行。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 170.637,
      "end": 184.632,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "new hotels"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是给 visitors 住的；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "an immense stadium"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是巨大的体育场；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Olympic-standard swimming pool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是达到奥运要求的游泳池。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 184.982,
      "end": 196.238,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文又说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They will also be building new roads and a special railway line."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "大事件不只要场馆，也要 transport，让人能到达、离开、换乘。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 196.588,
      "end": 205.18,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是地点和 deadline。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Games will be held just outside the capital and the whole area will be called 'Olympic City'."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 205.53,
      "end": 215.849,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "just outside the capital"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 near the capital, but not inside it。这个新区域会被叫作"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Olympic City"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 216.199,
      "end": 224.679,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接下来是两条项目 deadline。第一条："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Workers will have completed the new roads by the end of this year."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 225.029,
      "end": 233.605,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will have completed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 future perfect，意思是到了未来某个截止点时，这件事已经完成。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 233.955,
      "end": 239.955,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二条："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "By the end of next year, they will have finished work on the new stadium."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 240.305,
      "end": 249.345,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是项目经理的英语：by this year, roads done；by next year, stadium done。语法跟着建设时间表走。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 249.694,
      "end": 257.262,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是建筑升起和大家等待。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The fantastic modern buildings have been designed by Kurt Gunter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 257.612,
      "end": 267.684,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "have been designed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 present perfect passive，说明这些建筑已经有设计师了，workers 正在把设计变成真实建筑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 268.034,
      "end": 273.294,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everybody will be watching anxiously as the new buildings go up."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 273.644,
      "end": 285.8,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "go up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 buildings are being built，建筑慢慢建起来。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "anxiously"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是恐慌，而是又期待又紧张地盯着进度。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 286.15,
      "end": 295.149,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一层情绪来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We are all very excited and are looking forward to the Olympic Games because they have never been held before in this country."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 295.499,
      "end": 308.379,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课的落点不是“奥运会很热闹”，而是：a huge future event becomes a real city project, with buildings, transport, deadlines, and public expectation。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 308.729,
      "end": 311.249,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最容易误会的地方是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 311.599,
      "end": 315.902,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "以为它是在介绍奥运会项目，比如 running, swimming, football？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 316.252,
      "end": 324.592,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。但课文真正讲的是 hosting the Games。一个国家第一次办奥运会，城市要提前几年准备。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 324.942,
      "end": 328.296,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么先讲"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a great many people"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 328.645,
      "end": 339.845,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为 visitors 是建设的原因。人来了，就需要 hotels；比赛来了，就需要 stadium and pool；人群移动，就需要 roads and railway line。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 340.195,
      "end": 344.153,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Olympic City"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一个真的城市吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 344.503,
      "end": 352.503,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这课里，它是 capital 外面的一个 Olympic area。可以理解成专门为奥运会准备的新区域。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 352.853,
      "end": 359.51,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will have completed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will have finished"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么重要？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 359.86,
      "end": 371.58,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它们把 deadline 说清楚：到今年年底，道路已经完成；到明年年底，体育场工程已经完成。Future perfect 就是“到那个未来时间点，已经做完”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 371.93,
      "end": 376.357,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "anxiously"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是坏情绪吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 376.707,
      "end": 386.107,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是坏情绪。大家很 excited，但这么大的项目必须按期完成，所以会认真、焦急地 watching as the buildings go up。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 386.457,
      "end": 390.633,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Olympic Games will be held in our country in four years' time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 390.983,
      "end": 399.815,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As a great many people will be visiting the country, the government will be building new hotels, an immense stadium, and a new Olympic-standard swimming pool."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 400.164,
      "end": 404.196,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They will also be building new roads and a special railway line."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 404.546,
      "end": 410.09,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Games will be held just outside the capital and the whole area will be called 'Olympic City'."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 410.44,
      "end": 414.688,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Workers will have completed the new roads by the end of this year."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 415.038,
      "end": 419.43,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "By the end of next year, they will have finished work on the new stadium."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 419.78,
      "end": 424.1,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The fantastic modern buildings have been designed by Kurt Gunter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 424.45,
      "end": 428.506,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everybody will be watching anxiously as the new buildings go up."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
